==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: simvastatin
<hw>sim`va*stat"in</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>a chemical
substance (<chform>C25H38O5</chform>) having inhibitory activity on the
enzyme HMG-CoA reductase, and used in medicine to reduce cholesterol
levels in blood.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> synvinolin; MK-733; Zocor.</syn>⟦br⟧
